Package: python-ledmatrix
Architecture: all
Section: python
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, python-smbus
Suggests: i2c-tools, python-psutil
Description: Python library for the Pimoroni LED SHIM.
 LED SHIM tucks 28 RGB LEDs underneath a HAT or pHAT,
 it's ideal for showing notifications, patterns, or anything else!
 .
 This is the Python 2 version of the package.

